title: Candy Coated Christmas, Part 3
description:
We're back with Matt and Jake from Reality Gays podcast to finish out our recap of Candy Coated Christmas. Will Molly be able to sell the house her mom grew up in? Will she be able to resist Noah's rugged charm? And will she finally succumb to the Peppermint Hollow lifestyle?? We unpack it all.

Watch our supersized recap here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/60306575/
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
